kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171008%2Flarge%2F1507451298_8d06.jpg&h=18c9baf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n靚加加<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171008/large/1507451318_3a0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171008%2Flarge%2F1507451318_3a0a.jpg&h=0880c9f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171008/large/1507451339_a11f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171008%2Flarge%2F1507451339_a11f.jpg&h=b0002b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171008/large/1507451202_1e12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171008%2Flarge%2F1507451202_1e12.jpg&h=8b7e6c96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這天（8日）沙田日馬到尾段至有泥地跑，其中第七場四班泥地一哩為香港中華總商會盃，由熱門之一「靚加加」影相險勝，帶挈長腿女馬主史佩加捧盃，獲勝騎練為大摩及其馬房主帥貝湯美，兩人同樣新季首勝泥地，「靚加加」單Win及組合獨贏A2分別派51及23元。<br />\n<br />\n現年四歲的英國馬「靚加加」是繼第五場「紅駿之星」後，今午第二匹勝出的本港拍賣會馬，本身出自舊年香港國際馬匹拍賣會，由資深馬主史立德以350萬投得，送俾乖女史佩加當禮物。<br />\n<br />\n上季尾「靚加加」夥拍祈普敦贏同班同程泥地一哩開齋，勝出距離僅為馬頭位，今次仲激，「靚加加」排6檔沿途前置，直路透出後，臨尾田泰安座騎「威勢之寶」窮追不捨，「靚加加」受到嚴重威脅，猶幸最終影相險勝馬鼻位，從而錄得季內首捷，身穿連身淺藍色短裙的史佩加，賽後大晒長腿捧盃，搶晒風頭；亦造就大摩繼上次日賽囊括兩場三級賽後，再一次發揮盃王魅力。<br />\n<br />\n第七場二至四名依次是「威勢之寶」、「大步走」及「五星特工」，四重彩由四匹王牌馬組成，每注派9,144元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57306342&amp;category_guid=10860680&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57306342%26category_guid%3D10860680%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171008&d=sK2KRvT%2B3CmQkTl83yauWEjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=192f1602\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57306342%26category_guid%3D10860680%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171008&h=bb7b8ddf\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57306342&amp;category_guid=10860680&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171008</a>"}]}